		<div id="comment_body_64247796"><p>I am curious about what kind of daemon would notify the user of errors reported by the ECC code. I had to look at the system logs to see some ECC reported errors that the layer managed to fix. Sometimes even filling up the logs. There must be some kind of daemon for that right?</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64247796">

